title: Peter Schmuck Talks With Brett On The State Of The Orioles
text:
If player does not show correctly, click here to listen . Peter Schmuck part 1 If player does not show correctly, click here to listen . Peter Schmuck Part 2 If player does not show correctly, click here to listen . Peter Schmuck part 3 
Brett and Baltimore Sun Columnist Peter Schmuck debate the state of the Orioles and where the club is heading into the off-season. 
They talk about the pending free agents and can Buck Showalter and Dan Duquette work together?
